顏耀輝對曾俊華加入表示榮幸：「我們有著共同信念，深信保險業肩負著重要的社會責任。攜手合作下，我們希望能實踐理念，為香港大眾提供真正的保障。」而曾俊華則稱 Bowtie 團隊勇於嘗試，有難得的保險初心，對革新保險業充滿熱誠。「隨著科技進步，我相信市場需要一股新力量，將基本醫療保障帶給每一個香港市民。」<br />\n<br />\n2017 年在特首選舉落敗後，曾俊華非常活躍。度過「離職冷河期」後，他去年 6 月加盟一間主力金融科技的投資銀行「Ion Pacific」做副主席，7 月加入 IT 人張立申創辦、現時估值近 8 億元的 Benefit Vantage Limited（BVL），主營IP認證技術開發，現為公司的主要股東兼主席。9 月則成立非牟利組織「薯片叔叔合作社」，協助年輕人營運初創企業，<br />\n<br />\n他去年受訪稱，如今已不太留意政治，明言已進入人生另一個階段，無意再參選特首。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/finance/%E4%BB%BB%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%AA%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8-bowtie-%E8%B3%87%E6%B7%B1%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F-%E6%9B%BE%E4%BF%8A%E8%8F%AF-%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%9B%E9%87%8F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E8%2599%259B%25E6%2593%25AC%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%259A%25AA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8-bowtie-%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E5%2595%258F-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E4%25BF%258A%25E8%258F%25AF-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E9%259C%2580%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%2587%258F%2F&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m67%2FjevXO%2BySp3REELKrGah4%3D&h=4aab71ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E8%2599%259B%25E6%2593%25AC%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%259A%25AA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8-bowtie-%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E5%2595%258F-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E4%25BF%258A%25E8%258F%25AF-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E9%259C%2580%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%2587%258F%2F&h=974bfa86\" target=\"_blank\">http://thestandnews.com/finance/%E4%BB%BB%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%AA%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8-bowtie-%E8%B3%87%E6%B7%B1%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F-%E6%9B%BE%E4%BF%8A%E8%8F%AF-%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%9B%E9%87%8F/</a>"},{"pid":"696da5686aed41ef083b2dc9f5e82bd8ff23b10c","tid":1088247,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f42080df0a7b5619b050402564149619f659efb8","tid